 a thoughtful pose." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/8234919c-c007-42fa-b83f-25aee8effa69/essay-gettyimages-566353099.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-27019820-1 igZijh"><div class="sc-27019820-6 ioJvx"><div class="group z-[1] inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center peer gap-0 sm:gap-0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20" height="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="flex-shrink-0 hidden group-hover:inline">Save</span></div><p class="sc-27019820-3 kaLcRh peer-hover:hidden">essay</p><p class="sc-27019820-2 hXJDol peer-hover:hidden">Ethics</p></div><p class="sc-27019820-8 gmqcPE">Main character syndrome</p><p class="sc-27019820-9 cHrYLV">Why romanticising your own life is philosophically dubious, setting up toxic narratives and an inability to truly love</p><p class="sc-27019820-0 sc-27019820-10 jHrogk iRyBtd">Anna Gotlib</p></div><div class="sc-27019820-4 dNuwpm"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-4c328164-0 hOpepC footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-4c328164-1 bwTVbW kkIxMa"><div class="sc-1b596d24-0 ithRRD"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Ideas</a><a href="/videos" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Videos</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/about" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">About</a><a href="/contact" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Contact</a><a href="/support" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Support</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC gSiEIv"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/feed.rss" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">RSS Feed</a><a data-ga-select-prompt="aeon_footer_donate" href="/donate" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Donate</a><a href="/community-guidelines" class="sc-11b024c5-0 fQckeD">Community Guidelines</a></nav></div